name: Jacob Goldstein
summary: Jacob Goldstein is a 28-year-old, 5'10" tall software engineer originally from the Bronx. He graduated from Columbia University and is currently living and working in Los Angeles, California. Jacob values family, career growth, and education, and in his spare time, he enjoys cooking, traveling and reading. Being Jewish and liberal, Jacob is looking for a life partner with whom he can share a monogamous relationship. His preferred partner would also be looking to start a family in the future, just like him. He doesn't have any pets, he has occasional a drink but does not smoke or use drugs. As an active person, he appreciates a similar attribute in a partner. In terms of his preferred partner, he's seeking a straight woman between the ages of 24 and 30, who doesn't smoke, doesn't use drugs, leads an active life, and hopes for children in the future.
